Arabic-Presentation-Forms-A (U+FB50..U+FDFF)

concept-created: {2018-07-01}

description of U+FB50..U+FDFF

description::
· Unicode-block-name= Arabic-Presentation-Forms-A
· range= U+FB50|64336|ﭐ..U+FDFF|65023|﷿
· plane= plane.0
· quantity-of-code-points= 688
· quantity-of-chars= 611
· script= Arabic (609 characters), Common (2 characters)
· Preferred characters are found in the Arabic block 0600-06FF. This block also contains 32 noncharacters in the range FDD0-FDEF.
[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unicode_character_property#Block]
[ftp://www.unicode.org/Public/UCD/latest/ucd/]

char.Arabic-pedagogical symbols

description::
